Uvicorn
代码启动
if __name__ == "__main__": import uvicorn uvicorn.run(app=app, host="127.0.0.1", port=8000)
if __name__ == "__main__": import uvicorn uvicorn.run(app='main:app', host="127.0.0.1", port=8000, reload=True, debug=True)
命令行启动
uvicorn main:app --host=127.0.0.1 --port=8000 --reload
